Package gov.tak.api.cot.detail

Interface ICotDetailHandler2

  • public interface ICotDetailHandler2
    Implementations convert AttributeSet meta data to CotDetails and vice versa These methods should be called when converting to and from CoT for a specific CotDetail (usually supplied by AttributeSet metadata)
    Since:
    7.6.0

      • toItemMetadata

        ICotDetailHandler.ImportResult toItemMetadata​(java.lang.Object processItem,
                                              AttributeSet attrs,
                                              CotEvent event,
                                              CotDetail detail)
        Convert CotEvent CotDetail to AttributeSet metadata
        Parameters:
        processItem - The item being processed; owner of attrs
        attrs - AttributeSet
        event - AttributeSet's associated CotEvent
        detail - The detail associated with this ICotDetailHandler (read from this)
        Returns:
        ICotDetailHandler.ImportResult.SUCCESS if handled successfully ICotDetailHandler.ImportResult.FAILURE if handled but failed ICotDetailHandler.ImportResult.IGNORE if not handled or N/A ICotDetailHandler.ImportResult.DEFERRED if we should try again later

                    AttributeSet attrs,

                    CotDetail root)
        Convert map item metadata to a CoT detail
        Parameters:
        processItem - The item being processed; owner of attrs
        attrs - AttributeSet to read
        event - AttributeSet's associated CotEvent
        root - The CotEvent root CotDetail (add to this)
        Returns:
        True if handled, false if not

      • isSupported

        boolean isSupported​(java.lang.Object processItem,
                    AttributeSet attrs,
                    CotEvent event,
                    CotDetail detail)
        Check if this handler supports this item Used to filter out certain types from being processed by a handler
        Parameters:

        attrs - AttributeSet
        event - CotEvent
        detail - Associated CotEvent's CotDetail
        Returns:
        true if supported
